<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MusicMood</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <section class="intro">
            <div class="intro-overlay"></div>
            <div class="intro-text">
                <h1>MusicMood</h1>
                <p>Your personalized mood-based music recommendation system.</p>
                <a href="https://deployed-project-url.com" class="btn btn-primary">Try It Now</a>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="features" class="features">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 feature">
                    <img src="/images/user-authentication.png" alt="User Authentication" class="feature-image img-fluid">
                    <h3>User Authentication</h3>
                    <p>Secure and easy login to personalize your experience.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 feature">
                    <img src="/images/playlist-management.png" alt="Playlist Management" class="feature-image img-fluid">
                    <h3>Playlist Management</h3>
                    <p>Create, edit, and manage your playlists with ease.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 feature">
                    <img src="/images/mood-recommendations.png" alt="Mood-Based Recommendations" class="feature-image img-fluid">
                    <h3>Mood-Based Recommendations</h3>
                    <p>Get song recommendations based on your current mood.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="about" class="about">
            <h2>About MusicMood</h2>
            <p>MusicMood was inspired by a deep passion for music and the desire to enhance the listening experience for everyone. The idea came about when I realized how powerful music can be in influencing and reflecting our emotions. I wanted to create a platform that could understand and respond to our moods, providing the perfect soundtrack for every moment.</p>
            <p>This project began as a personal endeavor but quickly evolved into a collaborative effort. Our team has worked tirelessly to develop a system that leverages advanced algorithms to offer personalized music recommendations based on your current mood. This project is also a Portfolio Project for Holberton School, demonstrating our skills and dedication to creating innovative solutions.</p>
            <h3>Meet the Team</h3>
            <div class="row team">
                <div class="col-md-6 team-member">
                    <h4>Caleb Kech</h4>
                    <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/calebkech" target="_blank">
                        <i class="fab fa-linkedin social-icon"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/calebkech" target="_blank">
                        <i class="fab fa-github social-icon"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/calebkech" target="_blank">
                        <i class="fab fa-twitter social-icon"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 team-member">
                    <h4>Aymane Montassir</h4>
                    <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/hcktune" target="_blank">
                        <i class="fab fa-linkedin social-icon"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/hcktune" target="_blank">
                        <i class="fab fa-github social-icon"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/hcktune" target="_blank">
                        <i class="fab fa-twitter social-icon"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h3>Project Repository</h3>
            <a href="https://github.com/yourrepository" target="_blank">GitHub Repository</a>
        </section>
        <section class="about">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Project Progress</h2>
                <p>We have made significant progress in integrating the backend and frontend, completing user authentication, and initial playlist management. Our mood-based recommendation system is partially implemented.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="contact" class="contact">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                <form>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name">Name:</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">Email:</label>
                        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message">Message:</label>
                        <textarea class="form-control" id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
                </form>
                <div class="social-media mt-4">
                    <h3>Follow us on:</h3>
                    <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-social">
                        <i class="fab fa-github"></i> GitHub
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/yourusername" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-social">
                        <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i> Twitter
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://facebook.com/yourusername" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-social">
                        <i class="fab fa-facebook"></i> Facebook
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-social">
                        <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i> LinkedIn
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
